metadata.name: NFT.NYC 2023 VIP Pass 1/250
metadata.description:
NFT.NYC, the leading annual Non-Fungible Token event returns to New York City in 2023 (April 12-14).

Each VIP Pass is redeemable for a VIP Access Ticket to the April 2023 event PLUS:

- 1 x bonus piece of merch from OpenSea and other NFT.NYC partners.
- The first 50 VIP Passes minted will receive an additional VIP Access Ticket at no charge.
- Mints 51-250 have a 1-in-5 chance of receiving an additional VIP Access Ticket at no charge.

NFT.NYC 2023 Passes are modeled off the classic NFT.NYC official event pin, and are being made available exclusively on OpenSea. OpenSea has participated in NFT.NYC as its Foundational Partner since inception in 2018.

The holder of this NFT.NYC VIP Pass can now redeem their benefits via https://app.nft.nyc/token/0x62D97A70B130FD55Bf83cD2ABef70462c28540A8/1
